Since there's always people asking (here and elsewhere) when the next chapter will be out or if this has been abandoned...

Unlike his other stuff, Kakao only releases Setsuko for Comiket and the last one (C97) was December 2019.
C98 (scheduled for May 2020) was canceled due to Covid and C99 was originally scheduled for December 2020, postponed to May 2021 and then postponed AGAIN (technically, despite their numbering we missed 3 Comikets due to Covid already).

Currently, C99 is set for Dec 30-31, 2021 (unless Covid decides to mutate again or the situation changes otherwise), so expect the next chapter around then.
